name: EmptyFrameFittingOptions
shortdesc: Options for fitting content in an empty frame.

property.name: NONE
property.shortdesc: Does not use a fitting option.

property.name: CONTENT_TO_FRAME
property.shortdesc: Resizes content to fit the frame. Note: Content that has different proportions than the frame appears stretched or squeezed.

property.name: PROPORTIONALLY
property.shortdesc: Resizes content to fit the frame while preserving content proportions. If the content and frame have different proportions, some empty space appears in the frame.

property.name: FILL_PROPORTIONALLY
property.shortdesc: Resizes content to fill the frame while perserving the content's proportions. If the content and frame have different proportions, some of the content is obscured by the frame.
